{"tid":2070588,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指管有噴漆邊跑邊叫「跑快啲啦阿 Sir」　裝修學徒認襲警等罪　判刑 120 小時社服","createTime":"2020-06-19T08:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T09:56:31.000Z","uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75df1892807986fb02ad0c83ba72b75610fa40a2","tid":2070588,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年 10 月 26 日晚上，警方接報指沙田瀝源橋有人聚集，並塗鴉及貼海報。警員到場追截時，一名裝修學徒邊跑走邊叫「跑快啲啦，阿Sir」，被截後兩度推警員胸口，及後警員在其背囊搜出噴漆等物品。涉案學徒早前承認襲警及管有物品意圖摧毀財產 2 罪，還押 11 日，今日在西九龍裁判法院被判社會服務令120小時。裁判官強調，由於被告已還押一段時間，故今次判刑屬寬大處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E9%82%8A%E8%B7%91%E9%82%8A%E5%8F%AB-%E8%B7%91%E5%BF%AB%E5%95%B2%E5%95%A6%E9%98%BF-sir-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%AD%B8%E5%BE%92%E8%AA%8D%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91-120-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E9%2582%258A%25E8%25B7%2591%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%258F%25AB-%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%2595%25B2%25E5%2595%25A6%25E9%2598%25BF-sir-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25BE%2592%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591-120-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CxY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=71b113e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E9%2582%258A%25E8%25B7%2591%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%258F%25AB-%25E8%25B7